    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Loose, ankle-length trousers that are gathered or otherwise relatively tight around the ankles. They are worn by both men and women in India and Southeast Asia; often worn with a tunic-like over-garment.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
